@otto42</a>, <a href=\"http://punitsoftac/\">@punitsoftac</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sergeybiryukov\">@sergeybiryukov</a> et <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/xknown\">@xknown</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vous pourrez retrouver des explications compl√©mentaires avec les liens suivants&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2020/10/wordpress-5-5-3-maintenance-release/\">Annonce de sortie de WordPress 5.5.3 (en anglais)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/10/30/wordpress-5-5-3-release-some-technical-details/\">D√©tails techniques autour de la sortie de WP 5.5.3 (en anglais)</a></li></ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:97:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/2020/10/31/sortie-de-wordpress-5-5-3-details-techniques-importants/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"10\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"Questionnaire annuel 2020 sur votre utilisation de WordPress et r√©sultats de l‚Äôenqu√™te 2019\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:127:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/2020/10/28/questionnaire-annuel-2020-sur-votre-utilisation-de-wordpress-et-resultats-de-lenquete-2019/\";s:7:\"attr